Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  菠萝屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, pineapple
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:16.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1156,972)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.83,0:01:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, world
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.13,0:01:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,World?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.14,0:01:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话快说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talk to me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.05,0:01:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包裹到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Package, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然真的到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's finally here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.07,0:01:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢谢谢谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.02,0:01:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢  你是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼东东包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tennis Balls
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's "Tentacles"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.73,0:01:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来那就是章鱼哥的大名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's last name is "Tentacles"?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.21,0:01:49.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:49.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor guy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看章鱼哥新养的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check out Squidward's new snail
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.74,0:01:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:01:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来你收到的是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So that's what came in the mail
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来小蜗有新玩伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like Gary has a new little playmate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痴心妄想  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dream on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.80,0:02:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯纳丽绝对不准跟那头杂种玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't let Snellie here play with that mongrel mutt
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.45,0:02:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它可是纯种的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's a purebred
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包做的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A snail made out of bread
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.65,注释,,0,0,0,,[ bread（面包）与 purebred（纯种）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.88,0:02:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纯种意思就是血统高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Purebred means she's of the highest pedigree
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.77,0:02:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1124,746)}血统证明\N斯纳丽\N饲主  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连专属的证明文件都有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She even has her own papers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if you'll excuse us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.21,0:02:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯纳丽要开始训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snellie has to start her training
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛训练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Training?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备裤头村蜗牛比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For Bikini Bottom's snail race
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯纳丽这周天肯定能获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snellie will be winning this Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sunday?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.59,0:02:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来没办法让小蜗参赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I can't enter Gary in that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.40,0:02:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周天得洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sunday's laundry day
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之所以没法参赛  是因为小蜗是杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't enter Gary because Gary's a mutt
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, you got that right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你凭什么这么确定小蜗没法获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What makes you so sure Gary couldn't win that race?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,文件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Papers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:58.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,724)}饲主\N章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.97,0:02:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饲主  章鱼大脓包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Property of Squidward Pimples"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫东东包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Tennisball
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  斯纳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Snellie
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开始有点理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get the idea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说他家蜗牛比我家好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Squidward thinks his snail is better than mine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.69,0:03:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你想的跟我一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, are you thinking what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我得去找个蜗牛来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I should get a snail
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.37,0:03:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让它参赛  打败章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and enter it in that race and beat Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想的跟我一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想的是要让你参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about entering you in that race
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.96,0:03:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打败章鱼哥家的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and beating Squidward's snail
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来现在得开始训练了  小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're going to start our training now, ladies
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫你小妹妹是要让你丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call you a lady to humiliate and demean you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教练就用这种话来激励大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a motivational tool we coaches use
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know why
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天一定得把海绵宝宝揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I think I'll kick SpongeBob's butt tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草粉  吃了多长肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelp powder for muscle mass
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生蛋  老套路最好用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,raw eggs 'cause they're cliche
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,584)}钉子
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有钉子  增进体魄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and nails for toughness
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然得让你吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I expect you to eat this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是科学配方  保证让你明天获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's scientifically designed to help you win tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑得挺快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty good time
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快看我新养的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, check out my new snail
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你家蜗牛是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, your snail is a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它有着钢铁一样的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got nerves of steel
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大赛见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at the big race
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  竞争越来越激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, the competition's getting tough
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上开始高强度训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are going to start some serious training right now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  先从冲刺开始练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Gary, let's start with some sprints
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就各位  预备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your mark, set
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Gary, go
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.27,0:04:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利属于你  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all yours, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.20,0:04:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天就要比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the big race is tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要赢就得马上训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to start training if you want to win
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别白费口舌了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your breath, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.90,0:04:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家杂种绝对赢不过我家斯纳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That mongrel of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doesn't have a chance against Snellie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个好像忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you two seem to be forgetting
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正的赢家得主会是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who the real winner will be
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My snail
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that's a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.75,0:05:03.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:03.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它有着钢铁一样的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got nerves of steel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你站哪来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you standing on, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like I said
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用麻烦你明天来参赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't even bother showing up tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.49,0:05:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家蜗牛把章鱼哥给吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My snail's really got Squidward scared
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,huh, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟小蜗得去高强度训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary and I've got some serious work to do
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以逃得走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can run
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但绝对躲不掉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you can't hide, Squarepants
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  不能再闹下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Gary, no more fooling around
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来认真训练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get serious
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  快点动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary, move it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上上上上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, up, up, up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下下下下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down, down, down, down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,430)}蛞蝓兄弟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快快快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, faster, faster
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.77,0:05:37.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲冲冲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:37.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, push it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, push it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,壳给我动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move that shell
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary, move it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speed it up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.83,0:05:47.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:47.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快快快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move it, move it, move it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动起来动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stroke, stroke, stroke
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.95,0:05:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,420)}蜗牛比赛  牡蛎体育场
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛就要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're going to be late for the big race
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(266,772)}为快而生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1260,964)}我爱\N裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午好  女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎收看现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and welcome to our live coverage
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观赏今年春季必看经典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of this year's spring classic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第102届蜗牛赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the 102nd Running of The Snail
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天天气正好来举办这王牌运动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what a beautiful day for this sport of kings
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我刚好就是狂热体育迷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of which I'm a huge fan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的  我就只是个体育迷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I'm just a fan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来要找到座位坐的  结果这门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was on my way to my seat, the door was open
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起把目光投向场上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go down to the field
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看市长主持开幕式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to join the mayor for the pre-game ceremony
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.69,0:06:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来点燃象征体育精神的圣火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for the lighting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Torch of Good Sportsmanship
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家跟我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please join me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起欢迎蜗牛比赛第一届冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in welcoming snail racing's first-ever champion
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.47,0:06:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪电拉里卢西安诺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lightning Larry Luciano
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家请看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that, folks?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪电拉里卢西安诺  活生生的传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lightning Larry Luciano, a living legend
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正缓慢走向场地正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,slowly making his way center stage
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.74,0:06:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是这项运动的高光时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what a proud moment for this sport
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.22,0:06:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全场观众欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The crowd is going absolutely nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆贺拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, siree
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随时都会抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它已经快走四分之一的路程了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's almost a quarter of the way there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.97,0:07:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣火点燃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The torch is lit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the race begin
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  不得不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, SpongeBob, I must admit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不到你家杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that mongrel mutt of yours
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然还能找到起点线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would even find the starting line
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你输了再来恭喜  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save it for the loser's circle, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗现在状态好到不能再好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary happens to be in the best shape of his life
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会提醒现场医生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll alert the paramedics
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A burglar
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.75,0:07:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's the official
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经做好开赛准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ready to start here, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  斯纳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Snellie
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给这些普通蜗牛见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's show these common, garden-variety snails
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,优良种有什么本事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what superior breeding is all about
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Gary, listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下竞争会特别残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The competition is going to be fierce
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在处于劣势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the undersnail
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都不把你当一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's already counting you out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上场获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get out there and win
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给章鱼哥好看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so we can rub Squidward's big, fat nose in it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,训练那么久就为了这一刻  石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is what you've been training for, Rocky
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们才会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is why we're here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就各位  预备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your mark, get set
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,slither
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选手出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they're off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六号选手斯纳丽飞速起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number six, Snellie, rockets out of the starting blocks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把另外两名对手狠狠甩在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,leaving the other two competitors in the dust
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.27,0:08:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  斯纳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Snellie
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你行的  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got it, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干什么  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛都开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The race has started
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯纳丽都抢先你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You let Snellie take the lead
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start moving
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.90,0:08:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们训练那么久  都让你搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're blowing everything we trained for
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blowing it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Rocky
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想出发了再出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go when you feel like it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你有没有听到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别慢悠悠了  马上加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get the anchors out of your pants right now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别用那副表情看我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that look
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说马上加快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said now, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲起来  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get going, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲冲冲冲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go, go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七号选手已经起跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there goes number seven out of the starting gate
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选手状态似乎不佳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look so good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不行  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not good enough, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not good enough
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种状态可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do not like the look of this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's a race
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.04,0:09:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A race
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是聋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of 'em?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教练逼蜗牛逼得太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That coach is pushing that snail too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快快快快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, faster, faster, faster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七号选手好像爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like number seven has a blowout
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆炸两次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make that two, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头垫片也炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plus a blown head gasket
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的蜗牛还在冲向终点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the poor creature's still going for it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  可以不用跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you can stop now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它已经失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he's losing control
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想喘口气就喘吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can take a breath now if you want to, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它在失控地转圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's spinning out of control
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.09,0:10:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直冲着墙壁撞去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's heading straight for the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑住  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一位教练似乎奔向了跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of the coaches seems to have raced onto the track
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就自动取消比赛资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is an automatic disqualification
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:32.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,278)}终点
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子六号选手胜券在握了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like number six has this race all wrapped up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  斯纳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Snellie
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,场上只剩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's all you, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么不早说我逼你逼得太紧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just say I was pushing it too hard?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.11,0:10:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你早说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  为什么不早说我没在听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary, why didn't you tell me I wasn't listening?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你早说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My, oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.42,0:11:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位观众  这种情况前所未见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Folks, I have never seen anything quite like this
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来遥遥领先的斯纳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It seems Snellie, the leader
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调头回来安慰小蜗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just went back to comfort Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来咱俩要当亲家了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you and I are in-laws, eh, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是斯纳丽没赢  那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If Snellie didn't win, then
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,获胜者是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the winner is Rocky
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的纯种蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My purebred
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明明花了我一千七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which cost me $1,700
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却输给了一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lost to a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你特别想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how much you wanted to win
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我特地给你刻了奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I had the trophy engraved to you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.17,0:11:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.05,0:11:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛赛跑第一名奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The 1st Place Snail Racing Cup
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,献给  章鱼冬冬包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Presented to Squidward Tortellini?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(762,768)}冬冬包
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还算赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will I ever win?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁叫你昨天乱来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's for yesterday, Squarepants
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.79,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(273,270)\fs150\fsp40}蟹老板的\N{\fs40} \N{\fs150}中年危机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(335.802,504)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:14.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(377.802,584)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.67\pos(441.802,376)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(285.802,414)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(469.802,712)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您正在收听的是老K电台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got it tuned to KOLD
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夕阳红专属电台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K-OLD, the all oldies station
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a little something
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会让各位听众回忆往日美好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you may remember from the good old days
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好老
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're old
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好老
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're old
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老到发发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grumbling like a geezer
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.40,0:12:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾经红极一时  如今行将就木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yourself a-cracklin' like an old has-been
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看自己  老头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长着好多层下巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've got multiple chins
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你好老
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're old
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你做了早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made you breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  小豆豆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweet pea
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麸皮能让你做出这么多花样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you got creative with the bran today
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃药了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for the pill
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨吃药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate the pill
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.02,0:13:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you think I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,old?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸本来就该老
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddies are supposed to be old
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.24,0:13:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还是很酷  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm still cool, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你老爸酷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your old man is cool?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  大伙早都不会说酷这个字了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, no one says "cool" anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头子才会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's such an old-person thing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在都是说炫  举个例子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we say "coral," as in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你鼻子整得好炫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"That nose job is so coral"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炫  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Coral," eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一说就不炫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you say it, it sounds so uncoral
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我抑扬顿挫再念一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if I said it with a different inflection?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Co-ral
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.54,0:13:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不用去上班的吗  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to go to work or something, Dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.74,0:13:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你今天超炫  乖女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a coral day, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍妮  我是珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jenny, it's Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炫已经过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coral is definitely out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡思乱想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不老
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't old
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Pops
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马路就快过完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're almost across the street
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不要小孩来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need no snot-nosed little
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你看到那一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sorry you had to see that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能再慢点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you be any slower?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你转向灯都连开五个街区了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you've had your blinker on for the last five blocks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister, could you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把球扔回这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,throw the ball back over here?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要我跟你们一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's about I join you kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can keep it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么老头子老是这么扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do old people always have to ruin the fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.86,0:15:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别插队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No cutting
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟大家一样好好排队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to wait your turn like everybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,454)}裤头村公墓
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.17,0:15:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没你们那么老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't old like you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't old
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't old
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他有什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(614,822)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,452)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈  我的蟹黄堡味道怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, my Krabby patty tastes funny
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, no wonder
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经放老了  风干了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all old and dried out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟那边那位一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like that man right there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快扔到它应该去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, put that thing where it belongs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾堆里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蟹黄堡  我们同病相怜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, little patty, we're two of a kind
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都失去了往日的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've both lost our luster
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这口感比我这老头还柴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So that's what I taste like
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹堡王的员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Krusty Crew
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好晚上一起出去玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You all ready for the big night out tonight?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  一定会特好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's gonna rock
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to go crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经幻听了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm already hearing voices
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能别叫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.37,0:16:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们借一步说话吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's continue this conversation in private, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.67,0:16:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有谁在偷听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think some people are eavesdropping
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.50,0:16:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种家伙也太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how rude of some people
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.62,0:16:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那俩小伙子晚上要进城大玩特玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those youngsters are going out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a big night on the town
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整周都可期待今晚的到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward to this night all week
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Party
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说要先玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think we should do first?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪有什么不该先玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What shouldn't we do first?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're young
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有豪车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've got wheels
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前途无量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the world is our oyster
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你肩膀上面有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you got something on your shoulder
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来晃晃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hanging out?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.93,0:16:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:38.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无意间偷听到了你们的大计
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help overhearing your big plans
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道你们还能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I was wondering if you had room
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚再加一位来跟你们一起狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for one more crazy dude tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然能了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要跟我们一起玩吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you want to come with us, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到会这么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hadn't even crossed me mind
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.10,0:16:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But sure
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能会糟蹋了咱的气派
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He might cramp our style
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,气派
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Style
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看他知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see if he knows
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密酷小子握手式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the secret cool-guy handshake
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Course I know it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,old man
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.89,0:17:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.97,0:17:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine, and you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you're in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我不是很满意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm not happy about it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你通过测试了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You passed the test, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个小子八点钟来我家碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you boys show up at my house at 8:00
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先提醒一下你  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to warn you, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们总会光鲜亮丽地迟到几下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're always fashionably late
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,晚上八点零一分
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to party
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to party
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to party?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to party
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to party, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to party
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to party, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to par-tay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to par-tay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to par-tay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to par-tay, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to party
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to party, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to party
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸都被你丢光了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing me, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚有啥豪车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what kind of hot rod will we be cruisin' in tonight?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.81,0:18:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只开厉害的超跑  保证吸引美女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the most powerful chick-magnet in town
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水下碎心者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the underwater heartbreaker
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓跑美女还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's more like a chick repellent
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,座位才两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there's only two seats
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm your waters, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亲手来改装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I modified this little baby myself
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定现在小伙子都开这种车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what the kids are driving these days?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷小子才开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the cool kids
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们一定是迷路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys must be lost
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋大道就在附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doofus Drive is around the corner
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not lost
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带了指南针
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got my compass
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, dorks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, pals
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说这种话的早被咱打得满地找牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We used to beat people up for saying things like that
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个倒反天罡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's all topsy-turvy now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,440)}洗刷刷
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗刷刷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Wash
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种俱乐部取名越来越离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They sure are giving these clubs some crazy names
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不跟你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to tell you boys
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a little nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't been, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没登场好一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"on the scene" for quite a while now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟着我们玩就行了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just follow our lead, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤其就是要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And above all
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.90,0:19:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静耍酷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,keep it cool
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.99,0:19:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.15,0:19:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, gang
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's back
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起狂欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's party
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管怎样我都行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any port in a stor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是家洗衣店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a Laundromat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才叫像话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,色彩缤纷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The colors
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要看洗衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys want another rinse cycle?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm buying
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.80,0:19:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽说我跟大伙儿一样爱看衣服  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love staring at delicates as much as the next guy, but
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是  夜生活得多来点花样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's just that, I thought we'd see more of the nightlife
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少也让我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something that will give me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好疯一把  热血沸腾起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that wild and crazy, hot-blooded feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you know what I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然懂了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.75,0:20:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚咱们才刚刚开始放纵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is only stop numero uno on our night of debauchery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放纵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Debauchery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放纵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Debauchery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.75,0:20:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放纵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Debauchery?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.32,0:20:11.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:11.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高架底下捡垃圾哪热血沸腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of picking up trash under the highway as hot-blooded
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过既然小伙子都很投入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if it's what the kids are into
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.25,0:20:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So are you feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己在疯一把了没  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that wild and crazy feeling, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not yet
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  迟早会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you will
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.75,0:20:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你感觉到了没  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling it now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉到哪里热热的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a warm spot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.97,0:20:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,212)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你感觉到了没  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling it now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉到了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那个不能玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that's not a ride
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off of me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你感觉到了没  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling it now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你感觉到了没  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling it now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝有感乎  蟹掌柜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Art thou feeling it now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉到了没  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You feeling it now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008,736)}兔兔屋
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.73,0:20:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉到了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you feel it, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉到了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you feel it, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉到了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you feel it, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉到了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you feel it, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说  你们想知道我感觉到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you want to know if I can feel it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的想知道我感觉到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to know if I can feel it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.65,0:21:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I can feel it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想知道我感觉到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to know what I'm feeling?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉自己就像是个二百五
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling like a total barnacle-head
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们觉得这很酷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think this is cool?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮不潮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I with it now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.18,0:21:30.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都乐得这么明显了还看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys wouldn't know a good time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if it bit you in the aft end
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going home
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们一点都不酷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys ain't cool
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们很逊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're lame
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.09,0:21:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lame?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lame
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.46,0:21:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're nerds
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.27,0:21:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土包子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Geeks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.05,0:21:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Creeps
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外加幼稚鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And babies
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not babies
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算我老归老
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may be old, but even an old bag of shells like me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.38,0:21:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也知道你们整晚一件酷事都没做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knows that you haven't suggested
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one cool thing all night
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So good night to ya
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.83,0:21:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就要错过偷内裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you're going to miss the panty raid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.29,0:21:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.71,0:22:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就要错过偷内裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you're going to miss the panty raid
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Panty raid?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的是女的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're talking about girls, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那种女生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Girl girls?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.89,0:22:12.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:12.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.18,0:22:14.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说要翻箱倒柜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:14.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're talking about raiding their dressers
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷内裤对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for their underpants, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.07,0:22:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.12,0:22:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, count me in
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.44,0:22:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大功告成我就收回刚刚说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If this works, I'll take back what I said
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.93,0:22:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不当你们逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about you two being lame
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不逊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not lame
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, this is more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.90,0:22:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我们吧  老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give us some credit, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷内裤我们是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're panty professionals
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.90,0:22:37.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次都专偷这家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:37.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We score here all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.49,0:22:45.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蕾丝内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.49,0:22:45.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Frilly things
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中大奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We hit the jackpot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.25,0:22:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.67,0:22:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还真帮我大功告成了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You finally came through for me, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.15,0:22:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉自己又重返青春了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel young again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.15,0:22:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拿我裤子干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with my bloomers?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.64,0:23:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.30,0:23:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.64,0:23:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不早说要偷我妈家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me this was my mother's house?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.94,0:23:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也没问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是海绵宝宝跟派大星一手策划的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it was all SpongeBob and Patrick's idea
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我回房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to your room, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.16,0:23:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天亮之前都不准出门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're grounded for the rest of the night
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.32,0:23:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, pops
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.23,0:23:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你房间就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're almost to your room
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.40,0:23:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.95,0:23:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's all right, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实感觉重返青春了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I certainly feel younger
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.00,0:23:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.55,0:23:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  熄灯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, lights out
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.51,0:23:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mommy
